data.description: This home is being sold as-is, has bedrooms and a full bathroom on both stories. It features a large family room and large living room suited for entertainment. There is a solar system, new interior paint, some new floors and some upgrades in the upstairs bathroom. Fireplace, ceiling fans and ring doorbell. Driveway can comfortably park RV or several cars and there is new fencing leading to the backyard. Backyard features a large concrete slab suited for outdoor kitchen, space for new landscape and room to add an ADU. Court confirmation complete and family representative can accept offers. Submit offer with Preapproval letter and proof of funds to close. Offers subject to cross reference. There are several sources to learn about schools, entertainment venues, restaurants, beaches, parks, shops and professional sports' teams. Just minutes from downtown, the airport, Mission/Fashion Valley, and highways. xs Imperial, 69th and Skyline Drive.
